Version: 2.2.8
Release: alt1.1
Summary: EiskaltDC++ - Direct Connect client
License: GPLv3
Group: Networking/File transfer
Url: http://code.google.com/p/eiskaltdc/
Packager: Aeliya Grevnyov <gray_graff@altlinux.org>

Source: %name-%version.tar
